@startuml Campground Booking System
title Campground Booking System - Class Diagram

class User {
    -String name
    -String tel
    -String email
    -String password
    -String role
    -Date createdAt
    +register()
    +login()
    -getMe()
    -logout()
}

class Campground {
    -String name
    -String address
    -String tel
    +getCampgrounds()
    +getCampground()
    -createCampground()
    -updateCampground()
    -deleteCampground()
}

class Booking {
    -Date bookingDate
    -Number nights
    -ObjectId user
    -ObjectId campground
    -getBookings()
    -getBooking()
    -addBooking()
    -updateBooking()
    -deleteBooking()
}

' Relationships
User "1" -- "0..*" Booking : makes >
Campground "1" -- "0..*" Booking : has >

note bottom of Booking
  **Constraints:**
  - Max 3 nights
end note

@enduml